OL,3,CMan caught driving more than four
OL,4,Ctimes over drink limit disqualified
OL,6,FA man who was found to be more than
OL,7,Ffour times over the drink drive limit
OL,8,Fwhile travelling on the motorway has
OL,9,Fbeen disqualified from driving for 30
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FVincent Lime, of Caswell Close,
OL,13,FThurrock, was spotted on M4 eastbound
OL,14,Fnear junction 14 at 3pm on 6 December
OL,15,F'swerving between lanes' and 'nearly
OL,16,Fcolliding' with other cars.
OL,18,FWiltshire Police said they received
OL,19,Fcalls from three different members of
OL,20,Fthe public reporting Lime's driving.
