OL,6,FThe 36-year-old was arrested and later
OL,7,Fcharged with driving without a licence
OL,8,Fand drink driving.
OL,10,FOfficers waited at Membury Services
OL,11,Fbefore spotting the vehicle and
OL,12,Fwitnessing Lime swerving between
OL,13,Flanes, nearly colliding with other
OL,14,Fvehicles and changing speed
OL,15,Fsporadically.
OL,17,FThey stopped Lime and pulled him over
OL,18,Fto the roadside where he failed a
OL,19,Fbreath test, giving a reading of 148mg
OL,20,F- more than four times over the legal
OL,21,Flimit.
