OL,3,CMan caught driving more than four
OL,4,Ctimes over drink limit disqualified
OL,6,FPolice Constable Davis of the Roads
OL,7,FPolicing Unit, said: "I cannot stress
OL,8,Fenough how important it is to plan
OL,9,Fyour journey home if you're planning
OL,10,Fon consuming alcohol of an evening `
OL,11,Fthis includes any trips you are
OL,12,Fplanning on making the following day
OL,13,Fwhen you could still be over the legal
OL,14,Flimit.
OL,16,F"Never get behind the wheel of a car
OL,17,Fif you think you may be over the
OL,18,Flimit. The risk is never, ever worth
OL,19,Fit."
