OL,6,FOn 5 January, Lime appeared at Swindon
OL,7,FMagistrates Court where he pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to the charges. He was given a
OL,9,F30-month driving disqualification.
OL,11,FAs well as the disqualification, Lime
OL,12,Fmust also pay #85 Crown Prosecution
OL,13,FService costs and a #114 surcharge.
